Appliances
**********

**GET /appliances**

List my appliances.

Spec: ::

  Accept:
    $CT:appliances

Example: ::

  < GET /appliances
  < Accept: $CT:appliances

  > 200 Ok
  > Content-Type: $CT:appliances
  >
  > ...

**POST /appliances**

Create an appliance.

Spec: ::

  Content-Type:
    $CT:appliance-config
  | $CT:appliance-clone-request
  Accept:
    $CT:appliance-config
  | $CT:appliance-status
  | $CT:result
  Prefer:
    return=minimal

  Location:
    $URI

Example: ::

  < POST /appliances
  < Content-Type: $CT:appliance-clone-request
  < Accept: $CT:appliance-config
  <
  < ...

  > 201 Created
  > Location: /appliances/123
  > Content-Type: $CT:appliance-config
  >
  > ...

  < POST /appliances
  < Content-Type: $CT:appliance-clone-request
  < Accept: $CT:appliance-result

  > 201 Created
  > Location: /appliances/123
  > Content-Type: $CT:appliance-result
  >
  > ...

