Spec: ::

  Accept:
    $CT:appliance-result
  Prefer:
    return=minimal

  Status:
    200 Ok
  | 204 No Content
  | 409 Conflict

Example: ::

  < DELETE /appliance/123
  < Accept: $CT:appliance-result

  > 200 Ok
  > Content-Type: $CT:appliance-result
  >
  > ...

Example: ::

  < DELETE /appliance/123
  < Prefer: return=minimal

  > 204 No Content

**GET /appliances/:app**

Describe the latest version of an appliance.

Spec: ::

  Accept:
    $CT:appliance-config
  | $CT:appliance-status

  Content-Type:
    &Accept

Example: ::

  < GET /appliances/123
  < Accept: $CT:appliance-config

  > 200 Ok
  > Content-Type: $CT:appliance-config
  >
  > ...

